high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove.
Pick up the tea pot that's in front of you on the back left burner of the stove.
Take a large step to your right.
Fill the tea pot with water in the sink then shut off the tap.
Turn around and walk to the white table that's to the right of the fridge and stand in front of it facing the middle of it.
Put the tea pot under the one already on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a full tea pot on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the stove top.
Pick up the kettle from the stove top.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the kettle in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn around, walk forward past the refrigerator, then turn left and walk to the dining table.
Put the kettle on the dining table, in front of the other kettle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned kettle on a dining table.

high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the stove.
Pick up the kettle on the stove.
Go to the sink to the right of the stove.
Clean the kettle in the sink.
Turn around and go towards the wall, then turn left to face the white table.
Put the kettle on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle on the white table.
